      <title>大卫·布斯的《Dimensional》引发了人们对被动投资的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/david-booth-s-dimensional-stirs-up-old-passive-investing-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街一直认为被动投资的最大缺陷之一正在逐渐消失。Dimensional Fund Advisors 表示，情况不会这么快改变。]]></description>
