    <item>
      <title>巴西通胀再次加速，央行压力加大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/brazil-inflation-speeds-up-again-pressuring-central-bank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西的年度通胀率加速至目标范围的上限，这对央行再次造成打击，因为央行正努力控制蔓延至拉丁美洲最大经济体的价格压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/brazil-inflation-speeds-up-again-pressuring-central-bank</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 12:06:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行研究缩小利率走廊计划 警告债券风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/china-s-central-bank-studies-plan-to-narrow-its-rate-corridor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行表示，正在研究缩小短期利率波动区间的方案，扩大旨在更有效地引导市场的政策工具改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/china-s-central-bank-studies-plan-to-narrow-its-rate-corridor</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 11:16:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济放缓担忧抑制涨势，欧洲股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/european-stocks-rise-as-easing-recession-worries-boost-cyclicals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市周五上涨，因美国令人安心的数据有助于缓解人们对可能出现经济衰退的担忧，但区域基准指数本周仍小幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/european-stocks-rise-as-easing-recession-worries-boost-cyclicals</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 07:14:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西石油公司因税务协议意外亏损，但维持股息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/petrobras-maintains-dividend-after-tax-settlement-with-brazil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西国有石油生产商巴西石油公司（Petroleo Brasileiro SA）净亏损 26 亿雷亚尔（4.7 亿美元），令投资者感到意外，主要原因是首席执行官玛格达·尚布里亚德（Magda Chambriard）任职期间的首批业绩中出现了税务结算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/petrobras-maintains-dividend-after-tax-settlement-with-brazil</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 00:37:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
